  The goal of this code is to create a functional diagnostic tool that performs image analysis by extracting and quantifying the amount of color in an image. The app allows a user to capture or upload a photo, which is then rendered into numerical data to give a diagnostic test result. 
  Known Issues:
  Some images may appear rotated or flipped depending on the metadata of the original file and how the browser interprets the image's "orientation" tag.
